{"tid":1479751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818親親同胞行動","createTime":"2019-08-17T04:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T04:47:14.000Z","uid":195248,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2831d9cd2d2e1cb2011b2ed18d2719fa1e0bf5","tid":1479751,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"818明顯會有鬼混入<br />\n與其要比佢地借機搞事不如反客為主<br />\n倒輸入&ldquo;支持五大訴求&rdquo;係佢地到<br />\n將火撥返入大陸到<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n<br />\n1. 之前有post講過 &ldquo;搭膊頭 拎住支持牌&rdquo;比佢地影  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一定要殘體字</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 用港式普通話叫口號<br />\n&ldquo;禾敏之始商港撚&rdquo;<br />\n等佢地自己友拍片錄到用國語講野 等佢地自己都分唔到邊個係鬼 傳返入大陸既片都係普通話叫支持口號<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他方法請建議但請各位手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>千其唔可以出手</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>忍忍忍</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"41402fbc05909a89689e33c5ace5bf854f995fc5","tid":1479751,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"307953993d67942a8f65d72400f317478160ae4e","tid":1479751,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"fa9832ad936178a53fc9a35860d9ecd2b37df962","tid":1479751,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f5a81f297ab29dbb8e23066f2a0b2d6e7570cdd","tid":1479751,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"[相似的歷史] 今日台灣，明日香港。台灣由獨裁到民主40年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472821</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n<br />\n台灣歷史：<br />\n荒島&gt;日本現代化殖民&gt;民間好感&gt;劣化民國接管&gt;本地人成二等居民&gt;民主化<br />\n香港歷史：<br />\n荒島&gt;英國現代化殖民&gt;民間好感&gt;劣化中共接管&gt;本地人成二等居民&gt;？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n228事件 = 雨傘革命<br />\n雷震事件 = 梁天琦&amp;民族黨<br />